================================================================================
                            THIRD-PARTY ASSETS
================================================================================

The official Scout section logos ship in the theme as SVG files at
`assets/images/sections/{squirrels,beavers,cubs,scouts,explorers,network}.svg`,
downloaded by the theme maintainer from https://scoutsbrand.org.uk. Brand-asset
maintenance is centralised - Groups do not override these. Other images shipped
in the theme are generic placeholders that Groups override at the same path.

Those files are © The Scout Association. Their distribution within forks of this
theme is permitted only if the fork is being used to build a website for an
actual Scout Group, in line with The Scout Association's brand asset terms. 

Consult those terms for non-Scout-Group use.

The colour palette presets in data/palettes.toml use hex values published in
the Scouts Brand Guidelines (Our Colours, 2023). Hex codes are factual data
and are not themselves copyrightable.

The "Manrope" and "Nunito Sans" typefaces are bundled in the theme as woff2
files at assets/fonts/, under the SIL Open Font License 1.1, with each family's
OFL licence text alongside (OFL-Manrope.txt, OFL-NunitoSans.txt). Manrope is
Copyright 2018 The Manrope Project Authors; Nunito Sans is Copyright 2016 The
Nunito Sans Project Authors. They are self-hosted - not loaded from a font CDN
- so no visitor request reaches a third party.
